0922141555/https://www.news18.com/amp/news/movies/abhishek-bachchan-ileana-dcruz-begin-filming-ajay-devgns-the-big-bull-2310541.html|archive-date=22 September 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|}\n\n;Music videos\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" id=\"filmography\"\n|- style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Role(s)\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Performer(s)\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Album\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{Tooltip|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Pehli Dafa\"\n| 2017\n| {{Unknown}}\n| [[Atif Aslam]]\n| {{non-album single}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |  <ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.freepressjournal.in/entertainment/fall-in-love-with-atif-aslam-new-song-pehli-dafa/999310 |title=Fall in love with Atif Aslam new song 'Pehli Dafa' |date=7 January 2017 |work=[[The Free Press Journal]] |access-date=19 March 2018 |language=en-GB |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319151507/http://www.freepressjournal.in/entertainment/fall-in-love-with-atif-aslam-new-song-pehli-dafa/999310 |archive-date=19 March 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|}\n<!--Do not include future events. Only Films that has a source and has started filming,do not add films in Pre-production. See [[WP:CRYSTAL]].-->\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Film !! Award !! Category !! Result\n|-\n|| 2006 ||| ''[[Pokiri]]'' || [[Filmfare Awards South]] || Best Actress (Telugu) || {{nom}}\n|-\n|| 2007 ||| ''[[Devadasu (2006 film)|Devadasu]]'' || Filmfare Awards South || [[Filmfare Award for Best Female Debut&nbsp;\u2013 South|Best Female Debut]] || {{won}}<ref name=\"biography\">{{cite web|title=Ileana DCruz's Biography|url=http://www.koimoi.com/actress/ileana-dcruz/|publisher=Koimoi|accessdate=8 March 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418